Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八軒君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天5點起床辛苦麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在馬術部每天都是早上4點起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天開始4點起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別以為這樣子就能讓我認可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個修好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個打工的
